task.summary: Added simple asciimatics GUI. Text input not yet functional. Added initial support for map filters.
Implemented text input and command structure. Basic filtering now available. World regeneration from console now available.
added icon and height display toggling.
added icon and height display toggling.
Enabled editing generation variables from console
Began implementing basic Faction and Entity support. Reorganized project so model is Game rather than WorldMap. Implemented multicolor tile bg and icon support.
Added initial entity display. Misc map navigation bugfixes.
Unit movement now limited by radius
Movement selection more fluid, can escape unit movement and selection
Added information bar, turns (press n in input field), moves per turn, and nominally assigned the player a faction
No duplicate faction colors or icons; colors now easily visible
Unique entities now createable. Don't have abilities yet, but working on that.
